[9.756, "o", "\u001b[1;2;36m2026\u001b[0m\u001b[2m-\u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;36m03\u001b[0m\u001b[2m-13T\u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;92m08:59:23\u001b[0m\u001b[2m.\u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;36m551781\u001b[0m\u001b[2m+\u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;92m00:00\u001b[0m \u001b[1;31m[\u001b[0m\u001b[31mCRITICAL\u001b[0m\u001b[1;31m]\u001b[0m \u001b[36mresolver.assessment\u001b[0m — PRA final rules mandate mandatory adoption of the CRR III \r\nStandardised Approach for operational risk capital by \u001b[1;36m1\u001b[0m January \u001b[1;36m2027\u001b[0m, requiring material updates to ICAAP documentation, capital \r\nbuffer calculations, and regulatory notification within \u001b[1;36m90\u001b[0m days.\r\n"]
[0.001, "o", "  \u001b[31m⚠ CRITICAL\u001b[0m PRA final rules mandate mandatory adoption of the CRR III Standardised Approach for operational risk capital by \u001b[1;36m1\u001b[0m \r\nJanuary \u001b[1;36m2027\u001b[0m, requiring material updates to ICAAP documentation, capital buffer calculations, and regulatory notification within \u001b[1;36m90\u001b[0m \r\ndays.\r\n"]
[0.001, "o", "  \u001b[36mControls affected:\u001b[0m ISO-A.\u001b[1;36m5.29\u001b[0m, ISO-A.\u001b[1;36m5.30\u001b[0m, ISO-A.\u001b[1;36m6.1\u001b[0m, ISO-A.\u001b[1;36m8.8\u001b[0m, ISO-A.\u001b[1;36m12.6\u001b[0m.\u001b[1;36m1\u001b[0m, ISO-A.\u001b[1;36m18.1\u001b[0m.\u001b[1;36m1\u001b[0m, ISO-A.\u001b[1;36m18.2\u001b[0m.\u001b[1;36m1\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.001, "o", "  \u001b[2m→ Initiate a formal regulatory change programme immediately: assign an accountable owner to lead ICAAP remediation, retire AMA \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2mmodel documentation, recalculate capital buffers under the Standardised Approach, and file PRA notification of framework changes \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2mwithin the \u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;36m90\u001b[0m\u001b[2m-day window.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[1.005, "o", "\u001b[1;2;36m2026\u001b[0m\u001b[2m-\u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;36m03\u001b[0m\u001b[2m-13T\u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;92m08:59:24\u001b[0m\u001b[2m.\u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;36m560406\u001b[0m\u001b[2m+\u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;92m00:00\u001b[0m \u001b[1;33m[\u001b[0m\u001b[33mWARNING\u001b[0m\u001b[1;33m]\u001b[0m \u001b[36mregulatory.new_publication\u001b[0m — Resolution Planning: Minimum Requirement for Own Funds and \r\nEligible Liabilities \u001b[1m(\u001b[0mMREL\u001b[1m)\u001b[0m — \u001b[1;36m2026\u001b[0m Review\r\n"]
[0.300, "o", "\u001b[2mAnalysing: Resolution Planning: Minimum Requirement for Own Funds and E\u001b[0m\u001b[2;33m...\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[9.925, "o", "\u001b[1;2;36m2026\u001b[0m\u001b[2m-\u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;36m03\u001b[0m\u001b[2m-13T\u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;92m08:59:34\u001b[0m\u001b[2m.\u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;36m785931\u001b[0m\u001b[2m+\u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;92m00:00\u001b[0m \u001b[1;31m[\u001b[0m\u001b[31mCRITICAL\u001b[0m\u001b[1;31m]\u001b[0m \u001b[36mresolver.assessment\u001b[0m — The Bank of England's \u001b[1;36m2026\u001b[0m MREL review imposes binding capital \r\nadequacy obligations, resolution planning deliverables, and operational continuity requirements with a hard Q4 \u001b[1;36m2026\u001b[0m deadline and \r\nautomatic supervisory consequences for non-compliance.\r\n"]
[0.001, "o", "  \u001b[31m⚠ CRITICAL\u001b[0m The Bank of England's \u001b[1;36m2026\u001b[0m MREL review imposes binding capital adequacy obligations, resolution planning deliverables, \r\nand operational continuity requirements with a hard Q4 \u001b[1;36m2026\u001b[0m deadline and automatic supervisory consequences for non-compliance.\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  \u001b[36mControls affected:\u001b[0m ISO-A.\u001b[1;36m5.1\u001b[0m, ISO-A.\u001b[1;36m5.2\u001b[0m, ISO-A.\u001b[1;36m5.29\u001b[0m, ISO-A.\u001b[1;36m5.30\u001b[0m, ISO-A.\u001b[1;36m5.31\u001b[0m, ISO-A.\u001b[1;36m5.36\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.001, "o", "  \u001b[2m→ Escalate immediately to the Chief Risk Officer and Treasury function to initiate a gap analysis against current MREL holdings, \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2mcommission an updated resolution pack, and establish a Q4 \u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;36m2026\u001b[0m\u001b[2m compliance workstream with Board-level oversight.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
